<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Congratulations on Business Onboarding!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #343a40;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .accent {
            color: #28a745;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Congratulations, <%= business.user.name %>!</h1>
        <p>Your business onboarding process with <span class="accent">PayPhlet</span> is complete.</p>
        <p>You're now ready to start managing invoices and payments with ease.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing <span class="accent">PayPhlet</span>!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
